Name: AIR Battlefront
About the game: Immerse yourself in epic air battles with hundreds of enemies. AIR Battlefront is arcade fly combat shooter game based on WW2 theme. You play as a pilot of an aircraft of your country. The main objective - destroy as many enemy planes as possible. Features: Both First-person and Third-person view Fast paced mid-air battles Realistic control of an aircraft Full controller support Global leaderboard
